reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very small, won’t work for what we needed it for, so we’re changing out a table from a our home and keeping this one in our garage

I honestly have nothing bad to say about it. For the price, it is quite good. Extremely easy to set up and the instructions are clear. I bought the Amazon repackaged one with a “slight defect” and if I’m honest, I can’t find it haha. Has a great spot for my little books and is wonderful for small spaces as my photos show. Absolutely love this little table already and already have plans for a 2nd one.

reviews.reviewTitle: All the bits are there, looks easy to assembly
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This is very similar to another make Amazon sell that my son bought for his new house, going for that slightly industrial minimal look. He currently doesn't have a bedside table, night stand, thought this would be handy for him. I have checked the item over and it all looks to be there, came well packed the instruction booklet is clear. The wooden bit underneath is completely in tact. Every item has been wrapped and organised to make putting this together easy and ensure it gets to you in good condition.It looks to be a similar quality to the V****le make I mentioned, happy to recommend. Will fit into any little nook and crane to offer a slim console table, nightstand, shelf, hall table etc.
It's exactly what I was looking for, for this small space! It's sturdy and very easy to assemble, which took about 5 minutes.
